==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mimicker
<hw>Mim"ick*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
mimics; a mimic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An animal which imitates
something else, in form or habits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mimicry</ent>⟦br⟧
